<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.3.5">
<l>eḻilār tirumārvuk kēṟku mivaiyeṉṟu</l>
<l>vaḻakiya vaimpaṭaiyu māmāramuṅ koṇṭu</l>
<l>vaḻuvil koṭaiyāṉ vayicci rāvaṇaṉ</l>
<l>toḻutuva ṉāyniṉṟāṉ tālēlō tūmaṇi vaṇṇaṉē tālēlō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Vaiśravaṇa, generous and without fault, holds a beautiful necklace</l>
<l>[and] five beautiful weapons saying</l>
<l>“these are suitable for the sacred chest of he who is beautiful,”</l>
<l>he stands nearby, worshipping [you], tālēlō! Pearl-hued [Lord], tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
